#

French Bistro Burger with Herb Garlic Butter

$22.99
850 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

GourmetComfort FoodFrenchBistro

Description

A gourmet burger infused with herb garlic butter and topped with rich Gruyère cheese, accompanied by crispy pommes frites and a refreshing mixed green salad.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef (80/20): 1 lb
  • Gruyère Cheese: 4 slices
  • Butter: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tbsp, chopped
  • Fresh Parsley: 1 tbsp, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Burger Buns: 4
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Mixed Salad Greens: 4 cups
  • Olive Oil: 3 tbsp
  • Balsamic Vinegar: 1 tbsp
  • Dijon Mustard: 1 tsp
